c: 46
v: 34
t: Apui nuraka ek Neupeuleumoh Uroe nyan teuma apui nuraka Jikalon nyata le kaphe jadah Beuna atra nyoe geutanyong bak jih Jiseuot dum jih beuna sileupah Demi Po kamoe atra nyan beuna Geukheun treuk teuma rasa treuk di kah Sabab ka kaphe dilee keu Kamoe Rasa treuk jjinoe azeub that leupah